<item>
            <title>[LU-606] port bz24050 (Add alternative servers start order) </title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-606</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Issue:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;When newly created mdt registers itself, mgs erases all the logs for that particular fs, which fails client mount.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Fix:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Add alternative server start orders to enable MGS-&amp;gt;MDT(s)&lt;del&gt;&amp;gt;OST(s) as well as MGS&lt;/del&gt;&amp;gt;OST(s)-&amp;gt;MDT(s) order. &lt;/p&gt;
</description>
